---
title: Hearty Chorizo & Cherry Tomato Stew with Potato Mash & Parsley
description: Sit back and relax because this stew will come together in a flash. This bowl is like a warm hug with chorizo and veggies simmered in tomato sauce and poured on top of a fluffy pile of mashed potatoes. There’s nothing better than a stew that can warm you from the inside out.

